      "two_session_trace": "Session 1: A1 generates N3_1 and sends A1, {|N3_1|}shk(A1,A2). A2 decrypts, generates N4_1, and sends {|succ(N3_1),N4_1|}shk(A1,A2). A1 decrypts and sends {|succ(N4_1)|}shk(A1,A2). A2 generates N5_1 and sends {|N5_1|}shk(A1,A2).\nSession 2: A1 generates N3_2 and sends A1, {|N3_2|}shk(A1,A2). A2 decrypts, generates N4_2, and sends {|succ(N3_2),N4_2|}shk(A1,A2). A1 decrypts and sends {|succ(N4_2)|}shk(A1,A2). A2 generates N5_2 and sends {|N5_2|}shk(A1,A2)."
    }
  ]
